---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="關於我們 - 88茶葉" description="了解 88茶葉的尋茶故事與品質承諾。我們堅持產地直送，不滿意包退。">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-content">
      <span class="section-tag">關於我們</span>
      <h1>從茶山到杯中<br/>只為一杯台灣好茶</h1>
      <p>88茶葉，堅持親赴產地，嚴選海拔 1,000 公尺以上的頂級高山茶。<br/>沒有華麗的包裝，只有實實在在的茶香。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="section-inner story-layout">
      <div class="story-text">
        <h2>為什麼叫 88茶葉？</h2>
        <p>我們深信，喝茶是一件很純粹的事。但市面上的茶葉價格混亂、來源不明，讓許多愛茶人望之卻步。</p>
        <p>88茶葉的創立初衷很簡單：<strong>把產地真實的價格，與最純粹的高山風味，直接送到消費者手中。</strong></p>
        <p>我們與阿里山、杉林溪、梨山的在地茶農建立長期的契作關係。每年春、冬兩季，我們都會親自上山試茶、挑茶，確保每一批下山的茶葉，都符合我們嚴苛的標準。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-image">
        <img src="/images/hero-tea.jpg" alt="高山茶園" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Guarantee Section -->
  <section class="guarantee-section">
    <div class="section-inner text-center">
      <h2>我們的四大品質承諾</h2>
      <div class="guarantee-grid">
        <div class="g-card">
          <div class="g-icon">⛰️</div>
          <h3>100% 台灣高山茶</h3>
          <p>絕不混充低海拔茶或進口茶，每一口都是純正的台灣高山冷氣。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="g-card">
          <div class="g-icon">👨‍🌾</div>
          <h3>產地直送價</h3>
          <p>省去中間盤商抽成，把利潤回饋給茶友，讓您用合理的價格喝到頂級好茶。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="g-card">
          <div class="g-icon">🚚</div>
          <h3>免運費 / 貨到付款</h3>
          <p>全館免運費，支持貨到付款，讓您買得安心、收得方便。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="g-card">
          <div class="g-icon">💯</div>
          <h3>不滿意，保證退費</h3>
          <p>茶葉怕買錯？我們提供鑑賞期，只要喝不習慣，一通電話/一則 LINE 訊息，包退包換！</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Flavor Wheel Section (Placeholder) -->
  <section class="flavor-section">
    <div class="section-inner text-center">
      <h2>四大名山，風味各異</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--ink-muted);">我們整理了 88茶葉 主力茶款的風味特徵，幫助您快速找到命定好茶。</p>
      
      <div class="flavor-grid">
        <div class="flavor-card">
          <h3>阿里山春茶</h3>
          <div class="radar-placeholder">🌸 清幽花香<br/>🍯 極度甘甜<br/>柔順度：★★★★★<br/>喉韻：★★★★☆</div>
          <p>最受歡迎的大眾口味，花香顯著，完全不苦澀，每天喝都不膩。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flavor-card">
          <h3>杉林溪春茶</h3>
          <div class="radar-placeholder">🌲 竹杉冷香<br/>🏔️ 冷礦山氣<br/>厚實度：★★★★★<br/>回甘：★★★★☆</div>
          <p>行家最愛的「冷礦味」，茶湯厚實有層次，入喉後甘甜感持久。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flavor-card">
          <h3>石棹珠露 (VIP)</h3>
          <div class="radar-placeholder">💎 極致鮮度<br/>✨ 醇厚喉韻<br/>回甘：★★★★★<br/>香氣：★★★★★</div>
          <p>產量稀少的隱藏版，香氣高雅、喉韻極深，老饕指定的極致回甘款。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-inner">
      <h2>想找適合自己的茶？</h2>
      <p>點擊下方加入官方 LINE，由專屬客服為您量身推薦</p>
      <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/%40wgc0409f" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta-btn">
        加 LINE 諮詢 →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(26, 38, 24, 0.8), rgba(26, 38, 24, 0.8)), url('/images/tea-leaves.jpg') center/cover;
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }
  .about-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .story-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .story-text h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .story-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .story-image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  
  .guarantee-section {
    background: var(--parchment-warm);
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .guarantee-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .g-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  .g-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .g-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .g-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  .flavor-section {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: white;
  }
  .flavor-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .flavor-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--cream);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .flavor-card h3 {
    color: var(--gold-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }
  .radar-placeholder {
    background: var(--parchment);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .flavor-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(165deg, #1a2618 0%, #2d4228 40%, #1a2218 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .cta-inner h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: white; }
  .cta-inner p { margin-bottom: 2rem; opacity: 0.8; }
  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--ink) !important;
    padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
